casebody.data:
Joseph FRANKLIN, petitioner,
v.
Al LUEBBERS, Warden. No. 13-7419, 13A511. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 20, 2013. Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied. Justice SCALIA took no part in the consideration or decision of this application and this petition.
